title: 9 meses con Samanta
overview: A three-show special in which the presenter, Samanta Villar 's own pregnancy, was narrated, along with other exceptional pregnancy stories.During the program, Samanta recounted that she had been trying to get pregnant for more than four years, so she had to resort to egg donation.
